<br>
1) Soloing : Normal melees have trouble, casters are better<br>
<br>
2) Grouping : Melee own, caster suxx badly<br>
<br>
3) Raid : Its depends on the mob, overall casters own.<br>
<br>
Get a reality check ......<br>
<br>
Wiz are awesome against some mobs, and good against some<br>
others. The same goes out for melees. <br>
<br>
Velious = Melee Friendly mobs<br>
Luclin = Caster Friendly mobs<br>
<br>
Many casters are limited in their DPS by the inability of melees<br>
to compete with them on agro (raid mobs)<br>
<br>
When i do 20k with primal on I.V and a wiz 59k i doubt he<br>
needs more tuning... <br>
That wiz didnt even have FTs or Rend robe.<br>
<br>
Casters are better for -10min fights.<br>
Melees for +10mins.<br>
<br>
Casters need a big revamp on xp group situation, and maybe a<br>
small push in raid situation. But they are not as desperate as<br>
most of you pretend.<br>
<br>
